  "instructions": [
    "Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "Thread shrimp onto skewers, leaving a small space between each shrimp.",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together soy sauce, brown sugar, garlic powder, and smoked paprika.",
    "Brush the shrimp with coconut oil and then brush with the soy sauce mixture.",
    "Season with salt and pepper to taste.",
    "Grill the shrimp for 2-3 minutes per side, or until pink and cooked through.",
    "Brush with lemon juice and honey during the last minute of grilling.",
    "Serve immediately, garnished with chopped parsley."
